1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:35,940
♪Your secret, dangerous flaws♪

2
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I can stay close
without seeing through♪

3
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:45,610
♪As long as it's about love♪

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:46,870
♪No matter how absurd♪

5
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,450
♪I choose to get used to it♪

6
00:00:52,810 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Truth or lies, you decide what's true♪

7
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:00,800
♪I won't overturn it anymore♪

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,690
♪I cover my eyes and look♪

9
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:07,860
♪Is love an abyss or a trap♪

10
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:14,710
♪I only see the sparkle♪

11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:42,340
=Episode 17=
=Spitting the Most Hurtful Words=

13
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,310
Mr. Ji.

14
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,750
Truly worthy of Cangfeng's chosen heir.

15
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,560
You made a smart choice.

16
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,630
Did I have any other choice?

17
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,080
If I didn't choose this,

18
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,240
could my Cangfeng brothers and I

19
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,150
even leave Seronport alive?

20
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,240
If I refuse to serve you,

21
00:02:51,030 --> 00:02:53,000
then I'd be a traitor to Cangfeng.

22
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:56,430
Come on, don't say that.

23
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,750
It's that sly old fox Liang Zhaokun

24
00:02:58,910 --> 00:02:59,750
who set you up.

25
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,360
But don't worry.

26
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,030
Stick with me,

27
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,910
and you'll be well rewarded.

28
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:06,550
Come.

29
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,080
You handled the Suphan matter

30
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,280
perfectly last time.

31
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,800
Now that we're partners,

32
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,750
we could do something

33
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,470
even more exciting.

34
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,310
You know my bottom line.

35
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,120
Cangfeng is now

36
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,590
moving toward legalization.

37
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:32,590
I'm afraid...

38
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,870
Everything can change.

39
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,750
Legality in Seronport

40
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,750
is up to me.

41
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,120
Come.

42
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,400
Actually, Mr. Ji.

43
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,560
You could shift your mindset.

44
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:00,560
Instead of risking smuggling

45
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,560
and expanding to other markets,

46
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:05,960
why not focus on
Seronport's domestic market

47
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:07,680
and make it thrive?

48
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,840
How?

49
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,080
For example,

50
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,960
turn your current shipping routes

51
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,270
and properties

52
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,830
into profitable businesses.

53
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,560
Let me give you an example.

54
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:21,680
Like

55
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,800
your Li Island dock

56
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,830
could become a supply factory.

57
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,430
And your nightclubs

58
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:29,270
could sell goods.

59
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,800
If Li Island dock becomes a factory,

60
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,920
the fishermen won't agree.

61
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:41,240
They worship the sea
and depend on it to live.

62
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:44,300
You're asking me to smash their idol

63
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,910
and make me

64
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,430
become a wanted man hated by everyone.

65
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:56,680
Mr. Liang told me

66
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:59,480
you're his only wolf.

67
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:02,310
There's nothing you wouldn't dare do.

68
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,070
The riskier it is,

69
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:07,360
the more profitable it'll be.

70
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:09,150
Besides,

71
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:11,800
you can donate the money to the council.

72
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,720
You'll be a true standout by then.

73
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,240
Far better than

74
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:18,630
these small fries.

75
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:28,630
To show my sincerity,

76
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,830
I'll hand over everything

77
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,270
from Suphan's deal.

78
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,680
But I have one condition.

79
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,860
I know Liang Zhaokun

80
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,870
always wanted to be an insider with you.

81
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:39,770
He didn't make it,

82
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,070
so he started as a councilor.

83
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,600
But I'm different.

84
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,270
I don't care about being a councilor.

85
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:49,720
I want to be an insider.

86
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,190
People like us insiders

87
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,240
are all smart.

88
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:05,190
I think you fit perfectly.

89
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,190
Pleasure doing business.

90
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:09,910
Pleasure doing business.

91
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,240
I have one more thing

92
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,390
that I'd like to ask you.

93
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,870
I heard that Miss Hao by your side

94
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,000
is your...

95
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,240
What can she do?

96
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,390
She is nothing but

97
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,720
a woman who can't escape my grasp.

98
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,920
I'm relieved to hear that.

99
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:33,510
Actually I think

100
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:35,510
you and Shuyi are a perfect match.

101
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,980
If the two of you

102
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,430
could get married,

103
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,000
then naturally,

104
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,190
you'd become our insider.

105
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:47,790
Understood.

106
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:49,030
Come.

107
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,440
Come.

108
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:53,060
(Ji Zhijie's forced development
of the Li Island sparks public anger)

109
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:55,040
Miss Hao,
you'd better stay indoors for now.

110
00:06:58,510 --> 00:06:59,350
Why?

111
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:02,800
I went to Lianhua Street
for wontons this morning.

112
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,510
And got beaten.

113
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,760
I'm fine.

114
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:11,310
I only said it because I was worried

115
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,560
something might happen to you
if you went out.

116
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,400
Let me see.

117
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,070
Mr. Ji ignored the opposition

118
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,510
and seized land on the Li Island
for a factory.

119
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,120
It sparked public outrage.

120
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:22,680
Everyone is saying

121
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:25,630
Mr. Ji is Councilman Zhu's lapdog.

122
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,560
And we are Mr. Ji's lapdogs.

123
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,080
Speak up!

124
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,560
Who told you to attack?

125
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:35,600
Getting bold, huh?

126
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,360
- Who?
- Zhijie, Zhijie!

127
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,240
I told you to get land
for the councilor.

128
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,200
Yet you attacked the councilor.

129
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,200
What?

130
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,120
Are you just like those old fools?

131
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:48,600
You all want to rebel now?

132
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,240
Their men didn't just bully the locals.

133
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,630
They also beat up our brothers.

134
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:57,230
For people like that,

135
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,270
how could I serve them?

136
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,510
Come on, Feiying.
Are you a model citizen?

137
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:03,950
Are you a model citizen?

138
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:06,510
Like you've never done
anything ruthless?

139
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,600
And now you're preaching to me

140
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,390
about morality?

141
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:15,800
Who taught you that?

142
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,830
Who taught you that?

143
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,880
- Zhijie!
- You!

144
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,200
You.

145
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:24,870
You taught us since we were kids

146
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,120
to care for our brothers.

147
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,160
But now our brothers
are beaten so badly.

148
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:43,510
Am I not thinking of our brothers?

149
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,200
Am I not doing this for them?

150
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,870
Speak! Am I not doing this for them?

151
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,200
Fine.

152
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,790
You saved our lives.

153
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:56,550
We've long stopped fearing death.

154
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:00,150
If you say

155
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,550
all of this today

156
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:04,550
is what you want

157
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,320
and what you ordered,

158
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,120
then I, Feiying, will obey!

159
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,770
Yes, all of this is what I want!

160
00:09:10,770 --> 00:09:11,850
It's what I ordered!

161
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:12,840
Do you hear me?

162
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,320
Fine.

163
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,040
Fine.

164
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,320
Drag him to the kennel.

165
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,670
Then send him to Councilman Zhu.

166
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,320
Make him kneel and apologize.

167
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,770
Don't come back
if he doesn't forgive you.

168
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,440
You might as well kill me.

169
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:42,750
Zhijie.

170
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:45,030
It's really not
Feiying's fault this time.

171
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:46,200
Councilor Zhu's men went too far.

172
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,200
Say one more word.

173
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:48,200
And you'll end up like him.

174
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:52,390
Zhijie.

175
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:54,080
You still see me as your elder brother?

176
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,440
Don't think I don't know

177
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,320
Lianxing's men met with you

178
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:58,480
and gave you a truckload of gold.

179
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,120
Now you dare talk to me like this?

180
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,510
They did give that to me.

181
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,680
But I didn't take a single piece!

182
00:10:07,690 --> 00:10:08,670
If you want to leave,

183
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,120
get out of here right now!

184
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,840
They did give that to me.

185
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,320
But I didn't take a single piece.

186
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,080
Don't doubt us over some rumors.

187
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:23,510
Yes, I am suspicious.

188
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,630
Listen, Feilong.

189
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,440
All good things must come to an end.

190
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:38,920
Zhijie.

191
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,200
You're kicking me out too, right?

192
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,230
Yeah.

193
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,390
Leave.

194
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:46,350
You leave too.

195
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:47,750
And you.

196
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:49,470
All of you, leave.

197
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:51,590
Go abroad.

198
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,320
Go to Xingzhou Port.

199
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,910
Don't stay in Seronport.

200
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:57,390
I don't want disloyal people around me.

201
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,750
Starting today,

202
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:03,030
I won't tolerate anyone betraying me!

203
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:06,390
This isn't your style at all.

204
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,720
If you have plans or troubles,

205
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:10,960
just tell us directly.

206
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,440
Am I not clear enough?

207
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,240
This is exactly what I want!

208
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:16,750
Get lost, all of you!

209
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:23,510
Fine.

210
00:11:23,930 --> 00:11:24,920
You can tell us to get lost.

211
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:26,960
But I, Feilong,

212
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,240
will never leave Ji Zhijie and Cangfeng.

213
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,840
Feiying.

214
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:36,110
Let's go.

215
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,080
Oh my god.

216
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,550
How did Feilong offend him again?

217
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,440
But Feilong is Mr. Ji's

218
00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:56,440
most trusted man.

219
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:58,670
What has Mr. Ji been up to lately?

220
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,550
Why is he acting more like a tyrant?

221
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:02,630
It's fine.

222
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,230
Go do your thing.

223
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,790
I can handle it myself.

224
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,440
Ji Zhijie.

225
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:12,590
Ji Zhijie.

226
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:15,240
You never used to do this at home.

227
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:17,150
Or do this to your brothers.

228
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:18,080
People change.

229
00:12:18,090 --> 00:12:19,030
You know it better.

230
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,550
Do you have to be crueler
than Liang Zhaokun?

231
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,000
Stay out of my business.

232
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,080
I used to think

233
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,750
that you had
a bit more conscience than him.

234
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:31,270
You said it yourself, just a bit more.

235
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,270
Does a bit more or less really matter?

236
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:35,550
It's all the same to you anyway.

237
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:39,200
I used to think
you were Liang Zhaokun's blade,

238
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:42,750
but now I think you're scarier than him.

239
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,750
Ji Zhijie,
we don't have to be like this.

240
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,960
If this is because of me...

241
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,720
Hao Yu, don't flatter yourself.

242
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,120
Get this straight.

243
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,600
The only reason I still keep you around

244
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,510
is to torture you

245
00:12:58,670 --> 00:13:00,000
and make you pay.

246
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:09,670
You'd better behave and stay at home.

247
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:12,910
The more you try to ruin me,

248
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,960
the more I'll show you

249
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,960
how invincible I am.

250
00:13:23,900 --> 00:13:25,600
Sign the nightclub transfer papers
on the table.

251
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,420
(Neon Phoenix Lounge,
Transferor: Hao Yu)

252
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:41,740
(Transferee: Zhu Shuyi)

253
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,790
You coming out puts me in a tough spot.

254
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:51,390
Yu.

255
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,440
What are you doing?

256
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:56,750
Get lost!

257
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,840
Yu, Yu, you'd better go back.

258
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:02,470
Yu.

259
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:04,000
It's really just a standard transfer.

260
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:04,910
Once you sign,

261
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:05,770
Zhijie will be happy.

262
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:07,200
Maybe he'll give you other properties.

263
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,120
I thought it was a normal transfer.

264
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,440
But your reaction

265
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:12,030
makes me doubt it.

266
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,320
Yu!

267
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,160
Please.

268
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,150
Zhijie has changed recently.

269
00:14:19,170 --> 00:14:20,030
His temper is awful.

270
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:20,930
If he knows you're here,

271
00:14:20,930 --> 00:14:21,840
he'll kill me.

272
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:23,240
Look at Feilong and Feiying.

273
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,080
I'm terrified I'm next.

274
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,600
I made this decision on my own.

275
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:29,670
I'll take the blame if anything happens.

276
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:31,350
Help!

277
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,360
Where did that slut run off to?

278
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,720
- Help!
- Keep searching! Hurry!

279
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,200
- Check over here!
- Help!

280
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,040
Go!

281
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:41,840
Miss Hao.

282
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,440
Miss Hao, you must save me.

283
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:44,350
Xiaocui?

284
